Target personas:

Decision-makers (CTOs, architects, staff engineers):
- Understand why automated security configuration matters
- Learn how CIS benchmarks provide compliance framework
- See how HashiCorp portfolio of tools enforce security

Implementers (DevOps, platform engineers):
- Understand what CIS benchmarks are and why they matter
- Learn which tools apply security at each layer (images, infrastructure, applications)
- Get links to tutorials and documentation for implementation

